  <brief_title>Inactivity, Balance Problems and Fall Risk in Institutionalized Frail Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>Inactivity, Balance Problems and Fall Risk in Institutionalized Frail Elderly: What is the Impact of Benign Paroxysmal Positional Vertigo (BPPV) and Treatment Effectiveness?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
